    public class Dta114Reader
extends Dta113Reader
implements StataReader
    This class reads STATA data file of format 114. Stata versions and file formats Format Current as of --------------------------------------- 118 Stata 14 http://www.stata.com/help.cgi?dta 117 Stata 13 http://www.stata.com/help.cgi?dta 116 internal; never released 115 Stata 12 http://www.stata.com/help.cgi?dta_115 114 Stata 10 & 11 http://www.stata.com/help.cgi?dta_114 113 Stata 8 & 9 http://www.stata.com/help.cgi?dta_113 -------------------------------------- USAGE StataFile stataFile = new StataFile("C:\\java\\info\\Data\\STATA\\IMFFinReform.dta"); stataFile.getObservation(10);
    Author:
